{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943650/extras/FragPunk-TGA_End_Slate_2_EN.jpg?t=1739442864\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>FragPunk is a fast-paced 5v5 hero shooter with powerup cards that change the rules of each round! Choose your hero, your weapons, and pick from a selection of cards that dramatically change the rules of engagement!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Bend the rules with Shard Cards!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No two rounds of FragPunk are ever the same. Discover over 100 Shard Cards with an activatable selection that changes every round creating new and unique combinations that create infinite possibilities! Cards can amplify your jump height, reverse the roles of attackers and defenders, engulf your bullets in flame or turn them into chain lightning, and even may resurrect you and your team!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943650/extras/Steam-2-Cards.gif?t=1739442864\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Frantic 5v5 Hero Shooter!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each round lasts about 2.5 minutes, so get a move on! The short TTK means you have to aim well and react fast to win the fight. Pick between 12 heroes with diverse abilities, customize your weapon combination, choose your cards and get ready for a fight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943650/extras/Steam-1-Shooters.gif?t=1739442864\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Variety that fuels replayability</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pick your favorite hero from a selection of 12, each with their own unique abilities. Find your favorite guns among the 17 available, some which have special abilities, like shooting faster over time, bursts and more! Discover new hero, weapon and card combinations and develop your personal combat style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943650/extras/Steam-4-Variety.gif?t=1739442864\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Immersive Maps &amp; Vibrant Visuals!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prepare for rich map designs and mixed visual effects including collages, graffiti and a blend of realistic and stylized textures. Feast your eyes on bold colors, sharp shapes and dynamic lines to provide you with diverse visual experiences while the bullets fly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943650/extras/Steam-3-Maps.gif?t=1739442864\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2943650?t=1739442864","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943650/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739442864","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943650/08cffbd207e54a0f84ecfd1222c939de8e55c6c6/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739442864","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943650/08cffbd207e54a0f84ecfd1222c939de8e55c6c6/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739442864","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943650/extras/FragPunk-TGA_End_Slate_2_EN.jpg?t=1739442864\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>FragPunk is a fast-paced 5v5 hero shooter with powerup cards that change the rules of each round! Choose your h